    id: "ethics-amedex-0030",
    topic: "Ethics & Professionalism",
    subtopic: "Child sexual abuse - reporting and management",
    stem: `Fatima, eight years old, has been referred to you for an assessment of her unusual behaviour at school. She recently started exhibiting sexual mannerisms and showing her genitalia to her classmates at school. She is distracted in class, and her school performance is dropping. Which of the following is the most important action in this situation?`,
